{"tid":2189473,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有病徵者往檢驗 醫生憂播毒","createTime":"2020-09-05T02:24:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T03:04:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ebb6938805c444317235ca2fecd01b5dc8f26325","tid":2189473,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T02:24:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200905/PAZGU7QQS5AQ7IHKQAKBYRKLN4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200905%2FPAZGU7QQS5AQ7IHKQAKBYRKLN4%2F&d=RlZLtXxvTyjhSejQ4AJs44bCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=db0870c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200905%2FPAZGU7QQS5AQ7IHKQAKBYRKLN4%2F&h=b8df7fe2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200905/PAZGU7QQS5AQ7IHKQAKBYRKLN4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n有病徵者往檢驗 醫生憂播毒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/t3qQUPHvwhEaAcr-BIUXD4gTtKQ=/1970x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RT3SDPLKLZDT5IHXJYZHL7YIAQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Ft3qQUPHvwhEaAcr-BIUXD4gTtKQ%3D%2F1970x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRT3SDPLKLZDT5IHXJYZHL7YIAQ.jpg&h=f53a083f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■市民昨在西營盤李陞小學外排隊等候檢測。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】雖然政府建議有病徵市民切勿參加普及社區檢測計劃，不過有私家診所醫生透露，近日多名有傷風咳嗽等病徵求診者拒絕在診所接受武漢肺炎檢測，而選擇免費的全民檢測。有檢測中心採樣人員更指，中心入口僅攔截有發燒的參加者，但容許有咳嗽或喉嚨痛人士入內，憂慮帶來中心交叉感染風險。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：全民檢測 國產保護衣非醫療用  採樣醫護斥離譜<br />\n<br />\n有私家診所醫生向本報表示，近日多名有傷風或咳嗽等病徵人士求診，醫生向他們建議做武漢肺炎病毒測試，但病人表示已預約或想預約全民檢測，不需透過私家診所做檢測。該名醫生估計，箇中原因是全民檢測為免費，可節省在診所做檢測所需的150元行政費。<br />\n<br />\n該醫生呼籲，有病徵人士應盡快檢測，並非應等到預約日子才檢測，擔心若病人。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中心職員容許咳嗽人士進入<br />\n<br />\n在灣仔會議展覽中心的採樣人員亦指，檢測中心入口職員只攔截有發燒的人士。。。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君昨日在疫情簡報會表示，醫管局轄下有門診。。。<br />\n<br />\n政府發言人表示，檢測中心已張貼告示，提醒有意做檢測人士如出現有關感染病。。。"},{"pid":"c99616548faff4f9a98cab00aa84029dfafbec8a","tid":2189473,"uid":37836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T02:42:54.000Z","msg":"好快就會有檢測群組出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27a16fa671a0f80efbd3e630dbd9b62a7b9dc067","tid":2189473,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T03:04:50.000Z","msg":"就係想。邊個最想永續疫情？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}